metadata.name: Li3 Energy, Inc.
metadata.description: Li3 Energy, Inc., an exploration company, focuses on the acquisition and development of lithium and potassium mining projects in the Americas. The company focuses on exploring, developing, and commercializing its 49% interest in the Maricunga project covering 1,888 hectares of area located in the northeast section of the Salar de Maricunga in Region III of Atacama in northern Chile. The company was formerly known as Nano Dynamics Holdings, Inc. and changed its name to Li3 Energy, Inc. in November 2009. Li3 Energy, Inc. was incorporated in 2005 and is headquartered in Santiago, Chile.
